'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2832] on 9 October 2000 at 12:44:50 am'!"Change Set:		NebraskaEvents-arDate:			9 October 2000Author:			Andreas RaabSome fixes and encoder methods for events handled from Nebraska."!!UserInputEvent methodsFor: 'transforming' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:38'!transformBy: aMorphicTransform	"Transform the receiver into a local coordinate system."	position _  aMorphicTransform globalPointToLocal: position.! !!UserInputEvent methodsFor: 'transforming' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:38'!transformedBy: aMorphicTransform	"Return the receiver transformed by the given transform into a local coordinate system."	^self shallowCopy transformBy: aMorphicTransform! !!UserInputEvent methodsFor: 'transforming' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:37'!translateBy: delta	"add delta to cursorPoint, and return the new event"	position _ position + delta.! !!UserInputEvent methodsFor: 'transforming' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:38'!translatedBy: delta	"add delta to cursorPoint, and return the new event"	^self shallowCopy translateBy: delta! !!UserInputEvent methodsFor: 'encoding' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:17'!encodedAsStringArray	"encode the receiver into an array of strings, such that it can be retrieved via the fromStringArray: class method"	^{		type.		CanvasEncoder encodePoint: position.		CanvasEncoder encodeInteger: buttons.		CanvasEncoder encodeInteger: 0	}! !!KeyboardEvent methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:43'!isMouseMove	^false! !!KeyboardEvent methodsFor: 'encoding' stamp: 'ar 10/9/2000 00:14'!encodedAsStringArray	"encode the receiver into an array of strings, such that it can be retrieved via the fromStringArray: class method"	^{		type.		CanvasEncoder encodePoint: position.		CanvasEncoder encodeInteger: buttons.		CanvasEncoder encodeInteger: keyValue asInteger	}! !MouseEvent removeSelector: #transformBy:!MouseEvent removeSelector: #transformedBy:!MouseEvent removeSelector: #translateBy:!MouseEvent removeSelector: #translatedBy:!